    <text type="letter"> 
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01479.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1888-08-14">Tuesday Evng. Aug: 14&#8212;'88</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear TD&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Am here yet in the sick room&#8212;the Doctor thinks it best not to go yet&#8212;have
                had no set back&#8212;but remain horribly weak in legs &#38; body&#8212;(sometimes
                wonder whether that would remain for settled)&#8212;Thanks for the <hi rend="underline"
                    >Catlin</hi><ptr target="loc.01479_n1"/>&#8212;it is an <choice>
                    <orig>inexhaustable</orig>
                    <reg>inexhaustible</reg>
                </choice> mine</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01479.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <note type="editorial" place="right" resp="#unk">Written Aug 11/88 <hi rend="underline">T.D.</hi> by Walt Whitman</note>

        </body>
